texts.textentryhtml:
The Lane Collection. Victor Winthrop Newman (1860–?); [Anderson Galleries, New York, Newman Sale, February 2nd  and 3rd, 1920, lot no. 45, $45] [1]. Dickson Q. Brown (1873–1939); gifted to the Princeton University Art Museum, before 1943.

[1] Anderson Galleries Inc. Drawings by American, British, Dutch, Flemish, French, German and Spanish masters: the collection of V. Winthrop Newman... New York : Anderson Galleries, 1920, lot 45.
